# CakePHP Fields Plugin
Make returned fields in pagination configurable

## Background
In an Open API platform development, we need to support a more flexible way of managing 
which fields are expected to be returned in a query.

## Installation
- Clone from github : in your plugin directory type

	`git clone  git://github.com/iefreer/cakephp-fields-plugin.git fields`

- Download an archive from github and extract the contents into `/plugins/fields`

## Usage
- Include the component in your controller (AppController or otherwise)

	`var $components = array('Fields.Fields');`

- Set up actions/fields in fields/config/fields.php, it's self-explained


